703351f-a.title: Brooklyn: Brooklyn Avenue - Atlantic Avenue
703351f-a.text:
Brooklyn Avenue, east side, north from Atlantic Avenue to
Fulton Street. In the background appears the belfry of the Tomp-
kins Avenue Congregational Church.
VotJ11 September 12, 1940
P. L. Sperr
